The main.css file:

p.one {
    outline-color: #c0c0c0;
    outline-width: thick;
    outline-style: double;
    outline-offset: 1px;
}
p.two {
    outline: thick solid #ff00ff;
}
p.three {
    outline-color: #ff0000;
    outline-width: thick;
    outline-style: groove;
}

The web page with main.css file attached:

 <!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>CSS Outline Application</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="main.css">
    </head
    <body>
        <h3>CSS Outline Application</h3>
        <p class="one">Example 1: using outline property</p>
        <p class="two">Example 2: using outline property</p>
        <p class="three">Example 3: using outline property</p>
    </body>
</html>
